{"_path":"/maps/_docs/tech-docs/tech-docs","_dir":"tech-docs","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"技术文档","description":"技术文档与知识管理","original_path":"content/6.maps/_docs/tech-docs/tech-docs.md","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"domain"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Domain"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_docs/tech-docs/knowledge-flow"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Knowledge flow"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"教学设计的认知科学原理"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"教学设计的认知科学原理"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"叙事传输narrative-transportation"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"叙事传输（Narrative Transportation）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"用具体场景（如 YNAB 连接 Chase Bank）贯穿技术概念，而非抽象定义。\n人类大脑对故事的记忆强度是抽象信息的 6-7 倍（双编码理论）。\n情境模型让学习者在脑中\"预演\"使用过程，降低认知负荷。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"渐进式术语引入progressive-jargon-disclosure"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"渐进式术语引入（Progressive Jargon Disclosure）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"先让用户熟悉流程（\"你登录、选择账户、点击同意\"），再引入术语（\"这叫 resource owner\"）。\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"先体验后命名"}]},{"type":"text","value":"符合概念形成的心理机制——人类需要先建立直觉，再给直觉贴标签。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"认知缺口制造information-gap-theory"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"认知缺口制造（Information Gap Theory）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\"魔法发生了...我会剧透\"——故意制造信息缺口，触发好奇心。\n当大脑感知到\"已知\"与\"欲知\"的差距时，会产生认知性好奇，驱动注意力集中。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"情感标记emotional-tagging"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"情感标记（Emotional Tagging）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\""},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"BAD IDEA!!"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\"——全大写加双感叹号，视觉和情绪的冲击激活杏仁核，给记忆打上情感标签。\n神经科学研究表明，带情感色彩的记忆更容易从长时记忆中提取。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"双重编码dual-coding"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"双重编码（Dual Coding）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"让用户\"先看用户视角，再看开发者视角\"——\n同一信息通过两种不同的心理表征进行编码，显著增强理解和记忆。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"自我解释self-explanation"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"自我解释（Self-Explanation）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不断解释\"为什么要这样做\"（\"为什么不用 URL 传 token\"）。\n这种因果解释触发"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"自我生成效应"}]},{"type":"text","value":"——人对自己\"想明白\"的内容记忆更深刻。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.ducktyped.org/p/an-illustrated-guide-to-oauth","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"An Illustrated Guide to OAuth"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"domain","depth":2,"text":"Domain"},{"id":"教学设计的认知科学原理","depth":2,"text":"教学设计的认知科学原理"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_docs:tech-docs:tech-docs.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_docs/tech-docs/tech-docs.md","_stem":"6.maps/_docs/tech-docs/tech-docs","_extension":"md"}